Title: Switch
Plot: When an officer is shot to death on the freeway, the NCIS team takes upon the investigation. The first lead, a fact that the victim was leading a double life, takes them to a possible solution of the crime, but the tables are turned when the victim's dying message is discovered and it leads them to a totally different clue.
GuestStars: Merritt Wever, Geoffrey Lower, Brian Dietzen, Wilson Bethel, Richard Whiten, Andrew Caple-Shaw
